  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Your link to your patron allows you to serve as a conduit for radiant energy. You have Resistance to Radiant damage. Once per turn, when a spell you cast deals Radiant or Fire damage, you can add your Charisma modifier to that spell's damage against one of the spell's targets.</p><p>Additionally, when a creature succeeds its saving throw to avoid your Sacred Flame cantrip, you can cause their next saving throw made against your Sacred Flame cantrip to be done at Disadvantage until the end of your next turn.</p><p>Furthermore, whenever you roll dice to restore Hit Points to a creature with your Healing Light, you can roll the dice an additional time, and take the larger amount of healing.</p>",
      "chat": ""
    },
